The '''Large Egg''' and the '''Large Brown Egg''' are [[:Category:Animal Products|animal products]] obtained from [[Chicken]]s with sufficient [[Animals#Friendship|friendship]]. Large Eggs produce Quality [[Mayonnaise]] when used with a [[Mayonnaise Machine]]. For cooking, regular and large eggs may be used interchangeably.

Large Eggs can be hatched in an [[incubator]], which comes with a Big or Deluxe [[Coop]].

