==Bundles==
A Large Egg and Large Brown Egg are both options for the {{Bundle|Animal||y}}.

==Recipes==
Large Eggs work the same as regular chicken [[Egg|eggs]] in all recipes.{{#lsth:Egg|Recipes}}
==Tailoring==
Large Egg is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Cardigan]].  [[File:Shirt218.png|24px]]

==Quests==
Large Eggs are not used in any [[quests]].

